{"tid":1427055,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"警深水埗狂射催淚彈波及獸醫院 醫護慌忙抱貓徹夜走避ICU","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:46:08.000Z","uid":58307,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"35479493f05c268d307be1b1268be8ff2255d616","tid":1427055,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:49:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190806/59904756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59904756&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z4v2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=43db8060\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59904756&h=7c4ccb00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190806/59904756</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗警署外昨夜（5日）爆發警民衝突，警方站於警署內平台，無差別地向街坊、天橋、示威者發射催淚彈。單計高峯時期的一小時內，已經聽見最少40次催淚彈發射聲響。整夜催淚煙籠罩該區，尤是鄰近警署的荔枝角道及欽州街。不但市民飽受折磨，荔枝角道城大動物醫療中心正正位處戰線，一枚枚催淚彈墜落店門前，嗆鼻濃煙直攻貓病房，醫護急忙將貓隻抱到安全位置躲避。該院註冊獸醫怒斥警方只處一街之隔，明知發射催淚彈，卻從無任何通知。他亦指該院管理層只在事發後要求前線鎖緊門窗，但堅持要繼續接症，令全線當值人員感到非常不滿。《蘋果》正向該院查詢。"},{"pid":"e40803e5c2a23c410bb0941ed3f0ab7d04105619","tid":1427055,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"黑警嚴重危害貓狗生命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336647bdca8799f2b7dbe48092cf79e13b46b1ec","tid":1427055,"uid":275370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"喵喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8793e6bf7002ecc14124b7d271af369f465617e9","tid":1427055,"uid":69934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8945fd87c7e5c54ce95664d11192b6e73c7784f5","tid":1427055,"uid":60588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee78a9b8927125269575d5239ce88f724357a178","tid":1427055,"uid":265824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"好好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!"},{"pid":"9751299002dffb1a79e68fec743314b9c4f0a1b8","tid":1427055,"uid":206448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"貓狗大戰"},{"pid":"e34ae77be8066a275d9af4fe61c91786429b2232","tid":1427055,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"香港所有生物都畀支那迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da126b7cc9627af82c0882d9d8d5ca959a4bc8b","tid":1427055,"uid":58307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"貓義工張小姐一行四人在昨天（8月6日）凌晨於葵涌區某地盤工地前餵流浪貓，準備離開之際遇上兩輛警車，十多名防暴警察隨即下車。她形容防暴警察態度暴躁，大聲喝她「喺度做咩」、「唔好走」，更指接到市民報案「懷疑有人偷嘢」，要求他們男左女右分開，並出示身份證。<br />\n<br />\n點解關心流浪貓換來咁嘅結局？<br />\n<br />\n「點解我冇做錯事，咩武器都冇，佢哋都兇神惡煞，仲用枝警棍指住我哋。」張指，期間一度被嚇到喊。她續指，他們行裝輕便，身上只背著一個小型袋，手提著一袋貓糧及糧兜。張指，防暴警察查證後，「望兩望個地盤」，便收隊離開。<br />\n<br />\n「嗰度又遠離示威地點，我都莫名其妙。」她續指地盤位置偏僻，需要從葵涌轉小巴前往，沿路亦不會經過示威地點，對於突然遭防暴警察截查，感到莫名奇妙。張在一個月前，偶然發現地盤工地有10多隻流浪貓，於是開始定時到該處餵貓。由於白天太多人經過，貓咪會躲藏起來，所以張偏向在凌晨時分前往地盤：「點解關心流浪貓都可以換來咁嘅結局？」"},{"pid":"fe89dfc74b49bdd3cf15a587d14d713bf47ef3c7","tid":1427055,"uid":69934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGMvzX4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGMvzX4.png&h=3dd9e226&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4af687f30e932e65af0f33eeaa484bbb13399d7","tid":1427055,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}